WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.700
The paper distinguishes the trust-region concern from the off-policy concern. A fixed clip range is chosen before training.

00:04.700 --> 00:10.900
Equation 11 computes normalized effective sample size from the current batch of policy ratios. It falls when a few ratios dominate.

00:10.900 --> 00:17.800
Equation 12 uses the batch value in the score-function weight and the off-policy regularizer. The implementation maps those terms directly to code.
